data.description: A human trafficking case in San Francisco reached a rare conclusion this Thursday, with the arrest and charging of Kris Mike Nunez. Nunez, 19, faces multiple counts of pimping a minor over 16, pandering a minor over 16, human trafficking, and sales of narcotics. The San Francisco District Attorney.....
